    details:
      "\n<li>The Legends are back with an abundance of rewards and excitement!</li>\n<li>Accept ‘[The Legends Return!] The Legends Return!’ quest within the star event notifier on the left side of the screen.</li>\n<li>Upon entering the lobby, talk to Cynapse to select from either a Battle Mode or Practice Mode.<br>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Battle Mode:</strong> Battle with other players and obtain ranking scores.</li>\n<li><strong>Practice Mode:</strong> Enter alone to play test various avatars. You will not obtain ranking scores on Practice Mode.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>You must have equipped a weapon before you register in the queue.</li>\n<li>Your active buffs may disappear upon entry.</li>\n<li>By queuing, you will be assigned to a team with 2 other players. You will face off against another team with 3 players.</li>\n<li>Select your avatar! Each avatar will have a unique appearance and exclusive skills of its own.</li>\n<li>As you defeat monsters and characters from the other team, you will obtain EXP and Gold and level up to Lv. 15. <br>\n<ul>\n<li>Once you level up, you will receive the following perks:<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Acquire more skills</li>\n<li>Increase in Damage</li>\n<li>Increase in MaxHP/MaxMP</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Once you enhance your stats, you will receive the following perks:<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase in Critical Rate</li>\n<li>Increase in Damage</li>\n<li>Increase in MaxHP/MaxMP</li>\n<li>Increase in Attack Speed, Speed, and Jump</li>\n<li>Increase in the amount of HP/MP regained</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Once you’ve participated in 5 battles, you’ll be registered to the rankings.</li>\n<li>Rankings are calculated based on all worlds. Ranking score is shared within all your characters on the account.</li>\n<li>The name of the character that played last will be registered on the Rankings.</li>\n<li>Rankings will be determined based on the following in cases when characters have the same score:<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Have the most wins</li>\n<li>Have the least losses</li>\n<li>Obtained the relevant score first</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>As you accumulate wins, you will receive Cumulative Victory Rewards for each category once per account. Reward can be claimed by accepting ‘[The Legends Return!]</li>\n<li>Claim Your Cumulative Victory Reward!’ quest within the star event notifier on the left side of the screen.<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Cumulative Victory Rewards can be claimed until <strong>April 6 at 11:59 PM UTC</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>There are also Ranking Rewards for those that placed in rank 7,000 and above. The higher the rankings, the better are the rewards!</li>\n<li>Ranking Rewards can be claimed once per account.</li>\n<li>Ranking rewards will be distributed during the <strong>v.222 update maintenance on April 21</strong>. Rewards can be claimed until <strong>May 4 at 11:59 PM UTC</strong>.</li>\n<li>If you do not accept after being matched in the queue, you will receive a penalty of not being able to match or open the ranking UI for 30 minutes.</li>\n<li>If you do not move or attack for a certain time or leave in the middle of the battle, you will automatically lose and will receive a penalty of not being able to match or open the ranking UI for 30 minutes.</li>\n",
